Metaphor Manager Frontend
Copyright (c) 2024 Metaphor Manager Project

This software is part of the Metaphor Manager project, a system for managing and analyzing conceptual metaphors in text corpora.

The frontend provides a web-based user interface for:
- User authentication and profile management
- Project and document browsing and management
- Interactive metaphor annotation and editing
- Data visualization and export
- Collaborative review workflows

Built with:
- Next.js (React framework)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- TanStack Table
- Various React libraries and components

For questions about licensing or usage, please contact the project maintainers. 